@inherits LayoutComponentBase

<div class="page">
    <div class="sidebar">
        <NavMenu />
    </div>

    <main>
        <header class="cockpit-header" role="banner">
            <div class="cockpit-brand">
                <strong>TradingBot</strong>
                <span class="cockpit-subtitle">자동매매 콕핏 (읽기·연습)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="cockpit-safety-strip" aria-live="polite">
                <span class="badge badge-lock">실거래 잠김</span>
                <span class="badge badge-kill">긴급정지 ON</span>
                <span class="badge badge-mode">모드: dry_run</span>
                <span class="badge badge-live-off">실거래 허용 꺼짐</span>
            </div>
        </header>

        <article class="content px-4">
            @Body
        </article>

        <footer class="cockpit-footer">
            <small>
                시크릿·토큰·계좌 원문은 표시하지 않습니다. 실주문 버튼/HTTP는 없습니다.
            </small>
        </footer>
    </main>
</div>

<div id="blazor-error-ui" data-nosnippet>
    오류가 발생했습니다.
    <a href="." class="reload">다시 로드</a>
    <span class="dismiss">🗙</span>
</div>
